{"tid":1199733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能組到中立救援隊","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:07:24.000Z","uid":200062,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"332afe4930f1cebfd8985a3e4964e25e664de69d","tid":1199733,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"黎緊繼續有衝突 一定好多後生嘅受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇可能搵到香港medical嘅人 組到好似紅十字嘅救援隊 中立唔參與活動淨係做救傷工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如著白衣red cross 見有人受傷就救 放個救傷中心咁<br />\n<br />\n咁樣至少可以降低損傷 政府如果攻擊埋救援隊會有一定成本<br />\n同埋就算唔支持勇武嘅和理非 都會同情班後生仔學生受傷 有人肯出黎幫手就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫議員或者醫療組織幫手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1102db253b7bff03c4d6a88323559cbc01ed12a1","tid":1199733,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a06e000217b868af9e1de39151beb712dae311f4","tid":1199733,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"記者夠中立啦<br />\nTVB直頭幫警犬啦<br />\n咪又係比人打到仆街"},{"pid":"082187f6a65425492d07ea574da95d50a92c1a6e","tid":1199733,"uid":8290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b950f682db96db05d076544f5f3b034a0a2f86c","tid":1199733,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:43:43.000Z","msg":"認真 呢樣野會得到和理非泛民甚至中立嘅支持 好多人就算幾唔同意勇武都好 都會同情心痛學生受傷<img src=\